# Rust build artifacts.
/target

# Cargo.lock is intentionally NOT committed for this crate. Unlike the pinned
# harness (which commits its lockfile to freeze v0.91.0's transitive graph),
# this crate floats on upstream `main`: the compat-drift workflow resolves the
# dependency graph fresh each run so it actually tracks `main`. A committed lock
# would silently pin it and defeat the drift probe.
/Cargo.lock
